'''布倫丹·奧斯汀·羅傑斯'''（{{lang-en|Brendan Austin Rodgers}}，{{bd|1996年|8月9日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的內野手，目前效力於科羅拉多洛磯。他是[[2015年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2015年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]的選秀探花。
==職業生涯==
羅傑斯出身於足球世家，不過他在5歲時接觸了棒球。當時他是由他一個好朋友的父親來教他棒球，奠定了他的棒球基礎。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/draft/day-life-brendan-rodgers/|title=A Day In The Life: Brendan Rodgers|date=11 December 2014|work=BaseballAmerica.com|access-date=2021-03-03|archive-date=2017-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807071852/http://www.baseballamerica.com/draft/day-life-brendan-rodgers/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.orlandosentinel.com/sports/highschool/baseball/os-hs-lake-mary-brendan-rodgers-baseball-draft-20150404-story.html|title=Lake Mary shortstop nears chance to fulfill dream as baseball draft pick – Orlando Sentinel|author=Orlando Sentinel|date=4 April 2015|work=OrlandoSentinel.com|access-date=2021-03-03|archive-date=2017-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807073431/http://www.orlandosentinel.com/sports/highschool/baseball/os-hs-lake-mary-brendan-rodgers-baseball-draft-20150404-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[File:Brendan_Rodgers_(43580264231)_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]
羅傑斯在大二時就曾差點打出單季4成打擊率，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/108247032/top-draft-prospect-brendan-rodgers-crushes-homer-in-high-school-game|title=Top Draft prospect Brendan Rodgers crushes homer in high school game|work=Major League Baseball|access-date=2021-03-03|archive-date=2017-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171207102403/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/108247032/top-draft-prospect-brendan-rodgers-crushes-homer-in-high-school-game/|dead-url=no}}</ref>後來他在2015年大聯盟選秀被洛磯隊選走，成為那年的選秀探花。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_28277121/rockies-draft-brendan-rodgers-high-school-shortstop-no|title=Rockies draft Brendan Rodgers, a high school shortstop, with No. 3 pick|author=Nick Groke   The Denver Post|date=8 June 2015|access-date=2021-03-03|archive-date=2016-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330102230/http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_28277121/rockies-draft-brendan-rodgers-high-school-shortstop-no|dead-url=no}}</ref>他和球隊簽約後加入新人聯盟，打擊率2成73，並敲出3轟與20分打點。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20150626&content_id=132966538&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb&sid=milb|title=Third overall pick Brendan Rodgers homers, collects three hits in debut with Rookie-level Grand Junction Rockies – MiLB.com News – The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|work=MiLB.com|access-date=2021-03-03|archive-date=2016-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160324172021/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20150626&content_id=132966538&vkey=news_milb&fext=.jsp&sid=milb|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年，他在1A繳出2成81的打擊率，另敲出19轟與73分打點。2017年，他在高階1A及2A打球。打擊率為3成36，並敲出18轟與64分打點。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=663898#/career/R/hitting/2017/ALL|title=Brendan Rodgers Stats, Highlights, Bio - MiLB.com Stats - The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|access-date=December 9, 2017|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124014521/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=663898#/career/R/hitting/2017/ALL|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年季中，他升上3A。整年他的打擊率為2成68，並敲出17轟與67分打點。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=663898#/career/R/hitting/2018/ALL|title=Brendan Rodgers Stats, Highlights, Bio - MiLB.com Stats - The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|publisher=MiLB.com|access-date=October 11, 2018|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124014521/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=663898#/career/R/hitting/2018/ALL|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年5月17日，羅傑斯成功升上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.denverpost.com/2019/05/17/rockies-officially-call-up-brendan-rodgers/|title=Rockies’ Brendan Rodgers brings hot bat, sweet swing to his MLB debut|publisher=The Denver Post|author=Patrick Saunders|date=March 17, 2019|access-date=May 17, 2019|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125124005/https://www.denverpost.com/2019/05/17/rockies-officially-call-up-brendan-rodgers/|dead-url=no}}</ref>整年他出賽25場比賽，打擊率為2成24，另有7分打點。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/brendan-rodgers-rockies-promotion|title=Rox callup Rodgers nets RBI in 1st MLB at-bat|publisher=MLB.com|author=Thomas Harding|date=March 18, 2019|access-date=May 18, 2019|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107232111/https://www.mlb.com/news/brendan-rodgers-rockies-promotion|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年，羅傑斯在縮水賽季僅出賽7場比賽，打擊率連1成都不到，只有2分打點。
